{"TopicId":111158,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Ask the Mods questions about the Forums!","CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-28T17:01:51Z","PageNum":216,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Souptime","CreatedById":204451,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-21T03:35:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223896757\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221608513784\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. It\u0027s not against the rules for people under the age of 13 to have an account, it\u0027s just against the rules for them to reveal their age.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh ok\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nOh cool new page\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Entropian","CreatedById":205453,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-21T14:23:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223896746\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221608511608\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204451\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Souptime\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, Souptime said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nisnt it a little ironic that no one under 13 is allowed to have an account, yet unsuitable content for children isnt allowed either?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs far as I know the U13 requirement is from some US law saying that nobody under 13 can have directed-response presence online (like an account) unless there\u0027s some consent form filed.\u00A0 I think the unsuitable content ban makes the fora a politer and nicer place.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidSquid","CreatedById":196199,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-30T12:43:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi dear mods, if any one of you does speak french, maybe you can help here?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022209074\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9660920447\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/199084-huge-bug-with-fuel-tanks-and-engie/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:191px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI tried and failed, pretty sure it\u0027s a language/translation problem, not a technical one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-12-30T17:24:59Z\u0022 title=\u002212/30/2020 05:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 30, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by VoidSquid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-30T20:36:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027re on it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Commodore_32","CreatedById":200414,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-30T23:20:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anyone know what is this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022unknown.png?width=1025\u0026amp;height=105\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002210.24\u0022 height=\u0022105\u0022 width=\u00221025\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/771551196942958629/793978505339469874/unknown.png?width=1025\u0026amp;height=105\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-31T00:49:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve seen that a couple of times, too, \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/200414-commodore_32/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022200414\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/200414-commodore_32/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Commodore_32\u003C/a\u003E. I\u0027ve reported it and they\u0027re looking into it.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-01T03:58:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk I was just thinking about the forum games thread \u201Cdont click this\u201D and a question popped into my head. When a thread gets locked, is it possible to edit a post of your own as a regular member in a thread that is locked?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n215712312020\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-01T03:59:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223902082\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221609473495\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278020\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AlamoVampire\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, AlamoVampire said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk I was just thinking about the forum games thread \u201Cdont click this\u201D and a question popped into my head. When a thread gets locked, is it possible to edit a post of your own as a regular member in a thread that is locked?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n215712312020\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShouldn\u0027t be.\u00A0 The thread is locked now, can you edit your last post in it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-01T04:15:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223902084\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221609473584\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShouldn\u0027t be.\u00A0 The thread is locked now, can you edit your last post in it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor clarification, the thread has always been locked since \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/26298-ted/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002226298\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/26298-ted/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Ted\u003C/a\u003E locked in in 2013.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-01T04:21:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223902090\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221609474544\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor clarification, the thread has always been locked since \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/26298-ted/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002226298\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/26298-ted/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Ted\u003C/a\u003E locked in in 2013.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI guess that it is a glitch\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNope\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust kidding\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-01T05:07:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179753-geonovast/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022179753\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179753-geonovast/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Geonovast\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0nope. Truth be told before i asked i did not try. Upon seeing your reply i tried. Clocked the thing and all i saw was the options report and share. Thanks for the reply. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E230612312020\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Souptime","CreatedById":204451,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-06T23:50:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you guys have a discussion when you wanna open dont click this? or when a random mod does do you get a little angry you couldnt open it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CatastrophicFailure","CreatedById":57438,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-06T23:56:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223904872\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221609977045\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204451\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Souptime\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, Souptime said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you guys have a discussion when you wanna open dont click this? or when a random mod does do you get a little angry you couldnt open it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat are you talking about? That thread has never been unlocked. Not once. Ever.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Souptime","CreatedById":204451,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-07T00:00:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223904875\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221609977385\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257438\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CatastrophicFailure\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, CatastrophicFailure said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat are you talking about? That thread has never been unlocked. Not once. Ever.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\noh yes my misteak\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnother question: what is the angriest you\u0027ve ever seen someone on the forums?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-07T01:04:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223904876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221609977603\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204451\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Souptime\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Souptime said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnother question: what is the angriest you\u0027ve ever seen someone on the forums?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-07T22:54:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223904917\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221609981468\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThough I once saw a guy who actually went beyond that, all the way to \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eextremely\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/ZNGIcon2.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceman.Spiff","CreatedById":209133,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-07T22:57:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223905391\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221610060099\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022125662\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Snark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Snark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThough I once saw a guy who actually went beyond that, all the way to \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eextremely\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/ZNGIcon2.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat was the topic of discussion?\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nWas it something controversial, or maybe political? (those can get bad IRL)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-08T02:12:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223905394\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221610060253\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022209133\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spaceman.Spiff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, Spaceman.Spiff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat was the topic of discussion?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWas it something controversial, or maybe political? (those can get bad IRL)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was being a bit tongue-in-cheek:\u00A0 as moderators, we \u003Cu\u003E\u003Cem\u003Eoften\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/u\u003E have to deal with people who are upset-- usually with us, sometimes with other users.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOur favorite kind of moderating, of course, is when we get to help people-- for example, finding a post that a newbie has put in the wrong place, and moving it to where it will get the right sort of attention and responses.\u00A0 Or keeping an eye on the \u0022approval queue\u0022 so we can promptly approve the posts of new members who haven\u0027t racked up enough posts yet to be allowed to post \u0022unsupervised\u0022 (a measure that is, alas, necessary because of all the spambots and scammers out there, who like to prey on forums).\u00A0 Or getting to do fun things like recognize folks\u0027 contributions with Thread of the Month.\u00A0 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EI would say that \u003C/span\u003Eactually, \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Emost\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E of our moderating is of this \u0022good\u0022 kind, largely because the overwhelming majority of forum members are kind, helpful, friendly, people.\u00A0 This is a \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Enice\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E place, and most folks get along pretty well, and goodness gracious are we moderators thankful for \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Ethat\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E.\u00A0 It\u0027s why we stick around.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut unfortunately... sometimes things go sour.\u00A0 Even people who are normally \u0022good citizens\u0022 may be having a really bad day or something and can take comments personally, and end up in fights with other members, where tempers raise to the point of folks forgetting about the rules.\u00A0 Occasionally, not-so-nice people show up who deliberately troll or otherwise engage in hurtful behavior, and those are always un-fun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo we sometimes have to step in and correct such folks... and they are \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Enever\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E happy about it.\u00A0 Naturally so.\u00A0 Everyone always thinks of \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Ethemselves\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E as reasonable; this is human nature and is hardly surprising.\u00A0 In cases of conflict, it\u0027s always the other guy\u0027s fault.\u00A0 Which means, in turn, that on those rare occasions when we have to take action to correct a person... they\u0027re generally not going to be happy about it.\u00A0 We try to be respectful and matter-of-fact, but nobody likes being told they\u0027re in the wrong on anything, and some folks take it better than others.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo reactions run the gamut from apologetic to mildly annoyed to very angry to incandescent rage-- it really has more to do with the individual personality than with the actual topic of discussion.\u00A0 Some people have hotter tempers than others.\u00A0 We get yelled at, a lot.\u00A0 Which of course we don\u0027t enjoy, any more than you would-- but we knew that was part of the job when we volunteered.\u00A0 It can\u0027t really be helped, it goes with the territory, and it\u0027s worth it if it means we can help keep the forum nice for everyone else.\u00A0 It\u0027s why we do what we do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs for \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Ewhat\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E the topic of contention may be-- e.g. politics or whatever-- there are all sorts of things that folks can run up against; and in any case, out of respect for people\u0027s privacy, we can\u0027t give you any examples.\u00A0 Sorry.\u00A0 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever, if you just take a gander at the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/guidelines/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Eforum rules\u003C/a\u003E... well, we\u0027d prefer to have \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eno\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E rules if we didn\u0027t have to, so every forum rule that\u0027s there, is there because past experience has shown that it\u0027s necessary to prevent people from doing that thing.\u00A0 If there\u0027s a rule about it, generally that means that it\u0027s been done in the past, and was enough of a problem to need a rule about it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceman.Spiff","CreatedById":209133,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-08T02:33:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, for what it\u2019s worth I think you\u00A0guys do a good job.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-08T02:39:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs Snark says, our rules have been worked out as responses to problems that came up on the forum. If you look at something and think, \u0022That\u0027s weird. Why would they have a rule against that?\u0022 It\u0027s because that problem not only came up but got so bad that we had to ban people about it, so the rule was instituted to prevent having to issue more bans.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-08T03:06:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0essentially the forum rules are a \u201Cliving\u201D thing being adapted and updated as the behaviours and what not of the users changes over time?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n210601072021\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-08T03:21:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223905489\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221610075164\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278020\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AlamoVampire\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, AlamoVampire said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0essentially the forum rules are a \u201Cliving\u201D thing being adapted and updated as the behaviours and what not of the users changes over time?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n210601072021\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. We consider changes from time to time.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-08T03:27:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0out of curiosity how often are the rules adjusted to reflect new norms and are those adjustments announced or do they happen quietly? I personally do not recall seeing changes occur, I mean\u00A0I do not even recall even noticing when the rules adjusted to reflect Take-Two and their involvement with KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n212701072021\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n212801072021\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-01-08T03:28:19Z\u0022 title=\u002201/08/2021 03:28  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 8, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by AlamoVampire\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CatastrophicFailure","CreatedById":57438,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-08T04:36:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223905494\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221610076462\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278020\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AlamoVampire\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, AlamoVampire said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0out of curiosity how often are the rules adjusted to reflect new norms and are those adjustments announced or do they happen quietly? I personally do not recall seeing changes occur, I mean\u00A0I do not even recall even noticing when the rules adjusted to reflect Take-Two and their involvement with KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022tel:212701072021\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E212701072021\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022tel:212801072021\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E212801072021\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust one example,\u00A0Back when I was a youngun around here, I was officially scolded for posting a reaction meme \u003Cem\u003Esans text\u003C/em\u003E. Since then, that rule has been reconsidered, and wisely so. Picture is worth a thousand words and all... \u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-08T05:03:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIrregularly as needed. They were worked out pretty well in the early days, though. We haven\u0027t done much with them since then.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}